description: Good food on the go is hard to come by, but if freshly baked pizza is what you're craving, then we've got the food truck for you.Starting with dough handmade from imported Italian Caputo flour, every slice is sure to bring back that childhood love of pizza. Together with their exquisite pizza sauce, made daily, and their fresh toppings, you'll never want for a finer eating experience.Fast, fresh, delicious, and coming to a curb near you, what else do you nee to know? Gooroo's Wood Fire Pizza is definitely going to be your new favorite food truck!
name: Gooroo's Wood Fire Pizza
